OL,3,CTeenagers' deaths in bike crash led to
OL,4,Crioting against police, court hears
OL,6,FA riot was sparked by the deaths of
OL,7,Ftwo teenagers in a road accident after
OL,8,Frumours spread that they were being
OL,9,Ffollowed by the police, a court has
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FKyrees Sullivan, 16, and Harvey Evans,
OL,13,F15, died when their electric bike
OL,14,Fcrashed in the Ely area of Cardiff on
OL,15,Fthe evening of 22 May, 2023.
OL,17,FNewport Crown Court heard that rumours
OL,18,Fquickly circulated about the cause of
OL,19,Fthe crash which led to a hostile crowd
OL,20,Fdeveloping on the streets of Ely.
