OL,3,CTeenagers' deaths in bike crash led to
OL,4,Crioting against police, court hears
OL,6,FBricks and bottles were hurled at
OL,7,Fpolice, cars were set alight, and one
OL,8,Fofficer was struck by a petrol bomb in
OL,9,Fdisorder that lasted into the early
OL,10,Fhours of the following day.
OL,12,FMatthew Cobbe, prosecuting, told the
OL,13,Fjury the disorder followed the deaths
OL,14,Fof the two boys on Snowden Road.
OL,16,FHe said: "The emergency services were
OL,17,Fquick to arrive. The terrible news
OL,18,Ftravelled quickly, large crowds had
OL,19,Fgathered. It became necessary to set
OL,20,Fup cordons to secure the area.
