OL,6,F"Footage gathered of the events that
OL,7,Ffollowed showed the initial grief,
OL,8,Fdistress and anger within the crowd.
OL,10,F"Rumours began to spread about the
OL,11,Fcause of the collision, it wasn't long
OL,12,Fbefore the police were being blamed,
OL,13,Fwith rumours circulating that the boys
OL,14,Fwere being pursued when they crashed."
