OL,3,CTeenagers' deaths in bike crash led to
OL,4,Crioting against police, court hears
OL,6,FHe continued: "The hostility grew. For
OL,7,Fmany the anger turned to abuse,
OL,8,Fescalating to threats and violence
OL,9,Fdirected towards the police. Others
OL,10,Ffound it an irresistible opportunity
OL,11,Fto sneer and jeer and throw bottles
OL,12,Fand bricks, enjoying themselves as
OL,13,Fthey did so.
OL,15,F"Their emotions were a stark contrast
OL,16,Fto the grief and distress so obviously
OL,17,Ffelt by others. The hostility
OL,18,Fescalated rapidly, it wasn't long
OL,19,Fbefore the police were confronted by a
OL,20,Friot."
