OL,3,CTeenagers' deaths in bike crash led to
OL,4,Crioting against police, court hears
OL,6,FMr Cobbe added: "Dozens of people were
OL,7,Finvolved, bottles, bricks,
OL,8,Fplasterboard and more were hurled at
OL,9,Fpolice officers.
OL,11,F"Fires were set and fireworks thrown,
OL,12,Fcars were trashed, overturned and set
OL,13,Falight, a petrol bomb was thrown at an
OL,14,Fofficer, covering her in flames. It
OL,15,Fwas carnage for several hours."
OL,17,FThe court heard the police formed
OL,18,Fcordons around the crash scene to
OL,19,Fallow the emergency services to carry
OL,20,Fout their investigatory work.
