OL,3,CTeenagers' deaths in bike crash led to
OL,4,Crioting against police, court hears
OL,6,F"It is the prosecution case that each
OL,7,Fof these defendants played a part in
OL,8,Fthat riot, the roles they played
OL,9,Fdiffered, but they are joined by their
OL,10,Fparticipation, their common purpose
OL,11,Fand their unlawful behaviour," Mr
OL,12,FCobbe said.
OL,14,FHe said several other people had
OL,15,Fpleaded guilty to offences relating to
OL,16,Fthe rioting, which meant the jury
OL,17,Fcould be sure a riot had occurred.
