OL,3,CTeenagers' deaths in bike crash led to
OL,4,Crioting against police, court hears
OL,6,F"The fact that others have entered
OL,7,Fguilty pleas to riot does not,
OL,8,Fobviously, mean that these defendants
OL,9,Fare therefore guilty of riot.
OL,11,F"It means that in due course you will
OL,12,Fnot have to decide whether there was a
OL,13,Friot, your focus will be whether these
OL,14,Fdefendants were involved in the riot."
OL,16,FMr Cobbe said the whole community did
OL,17,Fnot "support or condone this
OL,18,Fextraordinary violence".
